# Document Templates

This document stores reusable templates for recurring project documents.

## Release Overview Template

```markdown
# Release {{version}}

## Summary
- Target date:
- Theme:
- Goal:

## Work Items
| No. | Item | Jira | Priority | Description |
|------|------|------|----------|-------------|
| 1 | Item name | AG-000 | P0 | Short description |
```

## Feature Note Template

```markdown
# Feature Name

## Background
- Why this work is needed
- What problem it solves

## Scope
- Core behaviors
- Main boundaries

## Documentation Output
- What docs were added or changed
- What follow-up docs still need to be written
```

## Review Checklist Template

```markdown
# Task Review Checklist

## Core Rules
- compatibility boundary
- input/output expectation
- major risk points

## Verification
- key scenarios
- linked documents
- known edge cases
```
